# Design system

Compose from `lib/core/theme/` + `lib/core/widgets/ds_*.dart`. No per-tab color forks.

Full reference: `docs/design_system.md`

## Default tab list pattern ★

**Any stacked row list on a tab** → `DsCategoryStyleList` family (`ds_category_style_list.dart`).

| Piece | Widget / token |
|-------|----------------|
| Section block | `DsCategoryStyleListSection(title:, children:)` |
| List shell | `DsCategoryStyleList(children:)` |
| Row | `DsCategoryStyleListRow(leading:, title:, subtitle:, trailing:, onTap:)` |
| Leading icon | `DsCategoryStyleListLeadingIcon(color:, icon:)` |
| Metrics | `DsCategoryStyleListMetrics` — **58px** rows, **64px** divider indent |
| Text | `DsCategoryStyleListTypography.title` / `.subtitle` / `.trailingMeta` |

```dart
DsCategoryStyleListSection(
  title: 'My Health',
  children: [
    DsCategoryStyleListRow(
      leading: DsCategoryStyleListLeadingIcon(color: c, icon: Icons.show_chart_rounded),
      title: Text(name, style: DsCategoryStyleListTypography.title),
      subtitle: Text(meta, style: DsCategoryStyleListTypography.subtitle),
      trailing: chevronOrValue,
      onTap: onTap,
    ),
  ],
);
```

## Other shells

- Tab scroll + header → `DsTabScrollView` / `DsTabHeader`
- Expandable report panels → `DsGlassCard` (not category list)
- CTAs → `DsPrimaryButton`

## Do not use for new lists

- `DsCategoryTile` — legacy card-per-item; superseded by `DsCategoryStyleList`
- Raw `Container` + manual dividers — wrap with `DsCategoryStyleList` instead
